@startuml patient_edit_request_state
!theme plain
title Patient Edit Request State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Created

Created --> PendingApproval : submitRequest()\n[Reception submits edit request]

PendingApproval --> ApprovedForEdit : adminApprove()\n[Admin approves initial request]
PendingApproval --> Rejected : adminReject()\n[Admin rejects request]

ApprovedForEdit --> ChangesSubmitted : submitChanges()\n[Reception submits proposed changes]

ChangesSubmitted --> ApprovedFinal : adminFinalApprove()\n[Admin approves changes]
ChangesSubmitted --> Rejected : adminRejectChanges()\n[Admin rejects changes]

ApprovedFinal --> [*] : processComplete()\n[Changes applied to patient record]
Rejected --> [*] : processComplete()\n[Request closed]

' Self-transitions
PendingApproval --> PendingApproval : addNotes()\n[Admin adds review notes]
ApprovedForEdit --> ApprovedForEdit : modifyChanges()\n[Reception modifies proposed changes]

' Notes
note right of Created
  Edit request initialized
  with patient ID and reason
end note

note right of PendingApproval
  Waiting for admin
  to review request
end note

note right of ApprovedForEdit
  Reception can now
  edit patient data
end note

note right of ChangesSubmitted
  Proposed changes
  await final approval
end note

note right of ApprovedFinal
  Changes applied to
  patient record
end note

note right of Rejected
  Request denied
  with reason provided
end note

@enduml